snippet.textDisplay: Finally summed up the courage to listen to this song after more than a year. This was to be my wedding song in 2015. The wedding never happened and its taken me forever to get over it. She really did take away every trace from me for the longest time. I now sit here, many many miles away from my home country, at 2 in the morning, thinking about her and hope that she is doing well. I know she'll listen to this song some time too. And if you do, know that I will always love you.

was a great scholar and a great sufi poet. He was a spiritual disciple

 originates khayal and tarana in music. His great invention was tabla..
